378
00:27:06,002 --> 00:27:08,842
You wanna stop being a dick, dad? Then just do it.

379
00:27:11,069 --> 00:27:12,287
I want to.

380
00:27:18,442 --> 00:27:20,992
I figured if Lucas moved in, I’d be my best self.

381
00:27:24,361 --> 00:27:25,591
The funny thing is…

382
00:27:26,844 --> 00:27:28,633
