385
00:27:55,077 --> 00:27:56,173
Nice try, dad.

386
00:27:58,001 --> 00:27:59,024
What else you got?

387
00:27:59,373 --> 00:28:00,709
This is how far we’ve come?

388
00:28:01,958 --> 00:28:03,360
You don’t believe when I’m sincere.

389
00:28:03,448 --> 00:28:05,025
History’s on my side, dad.

390
00:28:05,368 --> 00:28:07,394
No matter what you think, I would do anything for you.

391
00:28:07,544 --> 00:28:09,085
That’s what family does for each other.

392
00:28:09,208 --> 00:28:10,626
Even if you wife doesn’t understand that.

393
00:28:10,703 --> 00:28:11,839
